metadata.name: BaseMint Bud
metadata.description: The BaseMint Gang is a community-led brand fusing an animated series, gamification with rewards, custom music soundtrack, and experiences. The BaseMint Buds are a collection of 5,000 NFTs that allow you, the community, to join the Gang on their adventure and earn rewards along the way. The Gang needs your help to save the metaverse, Buds!
